## Topic Library

The library contains both offensive (red team) and defensive (blue team) topics, each mapped to a MITRE framework ID.

**Offensive topics** reference [MITRE ATT&CK](https://attack.mitre.org/) technique IDs (e.g. `T1566.001` for Spear Phishing with Attachments).

**Defensive topics** reference [MITRE D3FEND](https://d3fend.mitre.org/) countermeasure IDs (e.g. `D3-EHFI` for Email Header Field Inspection).

Sample topics from the library:

| ID | Title | Type | Difficulty |
|---|---|---|---|
| T1566.001 | Spear Phishing Attachment | Offensive | Beginner |
| T1055 | Process Injection Techniques | Offensive | Advanced |
| T1003 | OS Credential Dumping | Offensive | Intermediate |
| D1566 | Email Security Controls | Defensive | Intermediate |
| D1055 | Process Monitoring | Defensive | Advanced |
| D1003 | Credential Access Protection | Defensive | Advanced |
| D1021 | Network Segmentation | Defensive | Intermediate |

