## File Structure

Topicgen is a single self-contained HTML file. All logic, styles, and data are inline:

```
Topicgen
├── <style>           CSS — layout, card design, tab nav, difficulty badges
├── <body>            HTML — tab structure, card container, history panel
└── <script>
    ├── topicsDatabase    Array of all topic objects
    ├── generateTopic()   Picks a random topic (filtered by active tab)
    ├── renderCard()      Populates the card UI with a topic object
    ├── toggleSave()      Adds or removes the current card from the saved list
    ├── renderSaved()     Renders the Saved Topics tab content
    ├── toggleHistory()   Expands or collapses the history panel
    └── setupEventListeners()  Wires all button and tab interactions
```

